- 03:50:181 (1) - Is too late and 1/8 doens't sound right. Did some testing and the most accurate would prob be 1/5 grid ![](https://howrengar.s-ul.eu/3MzZd6eR)
- About 03:50:348 (2) - it also sounds late, but the most accurate snap would prob be on 1/16 grid ![](https://howrengar.s-ul.eu/meDcOJQQ) and it could be very tricky to hit it during gameplay. You could just keep it on the white tick but if you wanna be more accurate to the sounds, could use 1/16.

It would also be nice if you reduce the spacing between them, because the gap is pretty small and it could lead into a unreasonable combo break.
